org.matsim.withinday.controller

Class WithinDayControlerListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.withinday.controller.WithinDayControlerListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, MatsimExtensionPoint, ControlerListener, StartupListener

    public class WithinDayControlerListener
extends Object
implements StartupListener
    Attempt to realize functionality provided by WithinDayController by a ControlerListener (similar to what is done by the MultiModalControlerListener). Note: this class has to be registered as Controller Listener!

    cdobler
